snippet.title: Reptilian Rising Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Inspired by the anarchic humor and animation of Robot Chicken, and screwball synthwave comedies like Kung Fury, Reptilian Rising looks like no other game. 

Pop open that (virtual) box and marvel at the retro-styled miniatures. Watch them spring to life, animated in stop-motion style, battling until they run out of health and topple over as inanimate plastic once more.

For more information on Reptilian Rising visit the official site: https://www.reptilianrising.com

#ReptilianRising #GameTrailer
